,"tid":2370213,"uid":248044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a6eaa7c6a9adbe613daa7e25d3ca66f30ff45f0","tid":2370213,"uid":136606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"Velvet Underground嘅香蕉係1967年<br />\nPixies嘅Doolittle係1989年<br />\n樓主想聽邊個年代嘅作品多?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T13:18:02.000Z","msg":"兩個都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"其實我熟00年以後嘅indie music比較多，太舊嗰啲我自己都唔識，所以我隨便推幾張80年代嘅當做入門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Smiths - Queen is Dead(1986)<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/ed/The-Queen-is-Dead-cover.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fe%2Fed%2FThe-Queen-is-Dead-cover.png&h=786fa682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經典，八十年代最好嘅rock album，搖滾史其中一張最重要嘅作品。<br />\n<br />\nTalking Heads-Remain in Light(1980)<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/2d/TalkingHeadsRemaininLight.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F2%2F2d%2FTalkingHeadsRemaininLight.jpg&h=8ddbc09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNew Wave入面最豐富、最有想像力嘅作品，風格大雜燴，節奏歡快、脫俗。<br />\n<br />\nThe Cure-Disintegration(1989)<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b8/CureDisintegration.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fb%2Fb8%2FCureDisintegration.jpg&h=48ac67e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ngoth rock嘅始祖，唔好俾個cover嚇走，呢張嘅旋律都係一流。<br />\n<br />\nDinosaur Jr - You're Living All Over Me(1987)<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/de/Dinosaur_Jr._You%27re_Living_All_Over_Me.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fd%2Fde%2FDinosaur_Jr._You%2527re_Living_All_Over_Me.jpg&h=bb03de43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以同sonic youth齊名嘅noise rock band，個結他簡直無敵。<br />\n<br />\nGalaxie 500 - On Fire(1989)<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/04/On_Fire_%28Front_Cover%29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F0%2F04%2FOn_Fire_%2528Front_Cover%2529.png&h=b8715939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最早期嘅dreampop/shoegaze band，比起當時一堆grunge rock嚟講佢地成個節奏好慢，結他好清爽。<br />\n<br />\n仲有上面提到嘅pavement同sonic youth都係classic，樓主得閒都可以去連登indie post睇下，不過我自己都唔太敢喺入面留言......"}]}